    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Aromatic oil found in uncombined form in various parts of plants and employed for flavoring, perfume, disenfectant, and medicine.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
